      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "This is a rare find! We are thrilled to offer this vehicle in absolutely mint condition\u2014it truly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Every detail has been meticulously preserved, from the flawless exterior to the pristine interior. If you're looking for perfection and a car that has been pampered its entire life, this is the one for you!",
