    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive engineering, this vehicle has been maintained to an exacting standard. Featuring a clean profile and a documented service history, it offers a refined driving experience for the discerning owner. Its current state reflects diligent care, ensuring both reliable performance and aesthetic appeal. This is an exceptional opportunity to acquire a high-caliber vehicle that perfectly balances executive sophistication with long-term value.",
      "price": 34800.0,
