    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? This car has been such a trusty companion and is still in wonderful shape for its next owner. It\u2019s been well-loved and runs beautifully\u2014perfect for those daily commutes or fun weekend getaways. I'm honestly a bit sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019s going to make someone very happy! Feel free to reach out\u2014I'd love for you to come take it for a spin and see how great it feels on the road!",
      "price": 28900.0,
