    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-maintained daily driver that balances performance with comfort. The exterior finish presents beautifully with a deep luster, though a discerning eye will notice minor stone chips on the hood and a small hairline scratch near the trunk\u2014purely cosmetic and consistent with careful use. Inside, the interior is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in; the leather upholstery remains soft and supportive, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All technological features, from the responsive infotainment screen to the heated seats and backup camera, are in full working order. Mechanically, the car is sound, featuring a documented service history, a smooth-shifting transmission, and tires that were replaced just last season. It provides a quiet, confident ride and is ready for its next owner with no immediate maintenance required.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
